@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mtffyx(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v1 + tmp)
    v2 = v0
    v1 = (0.30 + (v0 - (tmp + 0.07 * v1 + 0.20)))
    v1 = (v0 + wp.sin((v1 + 0.31 / tmp + 0.09)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.10 - v1 + 0.51)) / (tmp - wp.abs(v0 + 0.56)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp((tmp + 0.44 + v2 + 0.31)))
    data[tid] = v0
